metadata.name: MyBuds #1
metadata.description: MyBuds is a hand painted generative NFT Collection created by the talented Tobias Rucka @tobias_rucka. This collection is based on a comic book written by Tom Jerabek @JerabekTomo23. MyBuds is a tribute to the amazing Hemp plant and its potential to serve as the solution for various ecological issues. MyBuds are hemp superheroes from OuterSpace! They fight evil, travel through the galaxies and help planets in difficult times! 7 different characters and more than 230 traits! Each Bud has a pass to the next adventures of our Roadmap. Thank you for being here!
